title: BRIEF-Discussions end between Ingenico Group and Worldpay
text:
BRIEF-Discussions end between Ingenico Group and Worldpay Sept 21 
Sept 21 Ingenico Group SA : 
* Indicates that the discussions which had been initiated with a view to potentially acquire Worldpay could not be completed and have been brought to an end Source text for Eikon: See also:
